<i>A mamka?</i>

24
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,790
<i>Nemôže prísť?</i>

25
00:01:42,810 --> 00:01:45,990
<i>Cnie sa mi za ňou.</i>

26
00:01:51,990 --> 00:01:53,700
<i>Ha-jon.</i>

27
00:01:55,960 --> 00:01:58,560
<i>Ockovi je to ľúto.</i>

28
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:05,930
<i>Ocko, neplač.</i>

29
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:10,090
<i>Ty si to predsa neurobil.</i>

30
00:02:10,090 --> 00:02:13,200
<i>Strýko Song-gju povedal,</i>

31
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:17,010
<i>že v televízii klamali.</i>

32
00:02:17,810 --> 00:02:21,990
<i>Presne tak. Strýko Song-gju mal pravdu.</i>

33
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:28,410
<i>Strýko Song-gju nemal ocka, tak nepoznal žiadne uspávanky.</i>

34
00:02:28,410 --> 00:02:29,820
<i>Takže?</i>

35
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:36,120
<i>Takže som mu spievala ja.</i>

36
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:40,750
<i>Áno? To bolo od teba milé.</i>

37
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:44,880
<i>Aj strýko Song-gju mi chýba.</i>

38
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:49,620
<i>Neskôr ho pôjdeme spolu navštíviť.</i>

39
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:52,730
